    "en": {
      "title": "Chinese Vice Foreign Minister meets Russian Ambassador",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chinese Vice Foreign Minister Ma Shaoshu met with Russian Ambassador to China Andrey Denisov in Beijing, the Chinese Foreign Ministry said in a statement on Wednesday.",
        "I said there that China is willing to strengthen strategic coordination with Russia and deepen cooperation under multilateral frameworks including the United Nations.",
        "Denisov said that Russia will improve communication with China to promote bilateral relations."
      ],
